### ⚡ Nordic Electricity Market Forecasting Platform

An AI-powered electricity market analytics platform built using real Finland electricity pricing data from the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform. This project focuses on electricity price forecasting, market volatility analysis, and time-series energy analytics using machine learning.

---

## 📌 Overview

Electricity markets are highly dynamic and influenced by:

* demand fluctuations,
* renewable energy generation,
* seasonal behavior,
* consumption patterns.

This project analyzes Finland’s real-world day-ahead electricity market data and builds a forecasting pipeline capable of:

* detecting market trends,
* predicting electricity prices,
* identifying volatility spikes,
* generating market intelligence insights.

The goal of this project is to demonstrate how AI and machine learning can support energy market analytics and forecasting systems.

---

# 🚀 Features

✅ Real Finland electricity market dataset
✅ Electricity price forecasting using Machine Learning
✅ Time-series energy market analysis
✅ Electricity price trend visualization
✅ Market volatility detection
✅ Hourly pricing behavior analysis
✅ Feature importance analysis
✅ Interactive Streamlit dashboard
✅ Energy analytics and forecasting insights

---

# 🧠 Machine Learning Pipeline

## Data Processing

* Timestamp conversion
* Missing value handling
* Feature engineering
* Data cleaning

## Feature Engineering

The following features were generated:

* Hour
* Day
* Month
* Weekday
* Year

## Forecasting Model

* Random Forest Regressor

## Evaluation Metrics

* MAE
* MSE
* RMSE
* R² Score

